value.title: The 2020 Election Collection: Claims About Mike Pence
value.excerpt: In his time as governor of Indiana and over his four-year term as vice president, Mike Pence has been in the middle of his fair share of rumors and fact checks. We’ve collected our own checks on his background and record here.
